    {
      "id": "PopularPost225381",
      "post_content": "@Donovan\\_Fabian: There are still some good snow creatures like [Adarkar Valkyrie](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Adarkar Valkyrie) and [Rimescale Dragon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rimescale Dragon). Nonetheless, they're less popular than Elves and Spirits, thus making this card more versatile than [Rend Flesh](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rend Flesh) and [Eyeblight's Ending](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eyeblight's Ending) and thus necessitating it's higher cost than those two cards (or, alternatively upping it to uncommon). Actually, I'm surprised they didn't up it to uncommon so less would be opened in packs for drafts where many of the creatures wouldn't be targetable by the spell.",
      "posted_by": "sarroth",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost225381\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">@Donovan_Fabian: There are still some good snow creatures like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Adarkar Valkyrie\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Adarkar Valkyrie\">Adarkar Valkyrie</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rimescale Dragon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rimescale Dragon\">Rimescale Dragon</a>. Nonetheless, they're less popular than Elves and Spirits, thus making this card more versatile than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rend Flesh\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rend Flesh\">Rend Flesh</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Eyeblight's Ending\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eyeblight's Ending\">Eyeblight's Ending</a> and thus necessitating it's higher cost than those two cards (or, alternatively upping it to uncommon). Actually, I'm surprised they didn't up it to uncommon so less would be opened in packs for drafts where many of the creatures wouldn't be targetable by the spell.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '225381'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy20957\">sarroth</span>\r\n                                (1/31/2012 9:18:55 PM)\r\n                            