      "id": "PopularPost262996",
      "post_content": "Pretty good, and fairly balanced card, actually. I consider many of black's anti-creature spells to be too powerful ([Doom Blade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom Blade), [Go for the Throat](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Go for the Throat), [Diabolic Edict](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Diabolic Edict), [The Abyss](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=The Abyss), [Terror](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror), [Sorceress Queen](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sorceress Queen) anyone?) taking away the fun of potential combat by removing every creature right after it hits the board.\n  \n   \nI actually would have preferred this card to be \"target non-wall creature is destroyed\".",
      "posted_by": "DrJack",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost262996\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">Pretty good, and fairly balanced card, actually. I consider many of black's anti-creature spells to be too powerful (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Doom Blade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom Blade\">Doom Blade</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Go for the Throat\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Go for the Throat\">Go for the Throat</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Diabolic Edict\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Diabolic Edict\">Diabolic Edict</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"The Abyss\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=The Abyss\">The Abyss</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Terror\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror\">Terror</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sorceress Queen\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sorceress Queen\">Sorceress Queen</a> anyone?) taking away the fun of potential combat by removing every creature right after it hits the board.\r<br/> <br/>I actually would have preferred this card to be \"target non-wall creature is destroyed\".</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '262996'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"Post